Package: rupclass
Type: Package
Title: Robust model-based classification based on impartial trimming and constraints
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Andrea Cappozzo, Francesca Greselin and Thomas Brendan Murphy
Date: 2019-04-04
Maintainer: Andrea Cappozzo <a.cappozzo@campus.unimib.it>
Description: Robust modification to the Model-Based Classification framework, employing impartial trimming and constraints on the ratio between the maximum and the minimum eigenvalue of the group scatter matrices. Both supervised (REDDA) and semisupervised (RUPCLASS) versions are included
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: mclust
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
